must include the email address connected to your account or other
personal details so to allow us to identify you.
5.6. If you choose to purchase a Premium Membership, your membership
will automatically renew on a monthly basis, unless you cancel your
subscription in accordance with this section.
5.7. If you terminate your Premium Membership, your account will revert
to a Basic Membership. If you want to terminate your Basic Membership,
